text: Winston Attong (born 19 March 1947) is a former Trinidad cyclist. He competed in the sprint event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Trinidad and Tobago male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Trinidad and Tobago Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Cyclists at the 1970 British Commonwealth Games
